{"tid":1763223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那記者打英國人被判刑 到底支那人柒夠未","createTime":"2019-11-30T07:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T07:20:38.000Z","uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0503ed9270e9dd3775d2af84669f305db4b152","tid":1763223,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"【央視記者孔琳琳襲擊罪成　判 12 月有條件假釋　賠受害人 2 萬港元】<br />\n<br />\n去年9月中國中央電視台駐倫敦記者孔琳琳在英國保守黨的研討會上，掌摑一名工作人員，英國法院昨日（29日）裁定襲擊罪名成立，判處 12個月有條件假釋，並須賠償受害人2115英鎊（約港元 2.1&nbsp;萬元&nbsp;），孔琳琳律師表示會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n央視駐倫敦記者孔琳琳早前出席英國保守黨人權委員會舉辦的論壇，期間大罵主辦方反中、分裂中國，並出手掌摑工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳事後被控普通襲擊，將於11月7日在伯明翰裁判法院提堂，法官指孔琳琳出手打人明顯構成襲擊，而推撞與會代表，則算是失去專業記者的冷靜後的激烈情緒反應，不構成犯罪，因此判處12個月有條件假釋，並須賠償被害人2115英鎊。<br />\n<br />\nSource 立場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%AD%94%E7%90%B3%E7%90%B3%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%88%A4-12-%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%81%87%E9%87%8B-%E8%B3%A0%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA-2-%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AD%2594%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%2590%25B3%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4-12-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%2587%258B-%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA-2-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=4a165019\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AD%2594%25E7%2590%25B3%25E7%2590%25B3%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%2588%25A4-12-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2581%2587%25E9%2587%258B-%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA-2-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583%2F&h=562e2060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%AD%94%E7%90%B3%E7%90%B3%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%88%A4-12-%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%81%87%E9%87%8B-%E8%B3%A0%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA-2-%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83/</a>"},{"pid":"078310bb2414cdc62d2b9f68e08767bfcaa8377a","tid":1763223,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"衰遠必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}